"\n"
"          Dear Mentors and Mentorees, 👩‍🏫👨‍🎓\n"
"          <br/>\n"
"          First of all, the Projects team would like to warmly congratulate "
"you for embarking on your mentorship journey. It’s sure to be filled with "
"exciting discoveries and achievements!\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"          Benvolguts Mentors i Mentoritzats, 👩‍🏫👨‍🎓\n"
"          <br/>\n"
"          Primer de tot, l'equip de Projectes us vol felicitar efusivament "
"per iniciar el vostre viatge de mentoria. Segur que estarà ple de "
"descobertes i èxits emocionants!\n"
"          "

